description:
The Season 12 official tag season has yet to start and team captains have yet to be named. For now we give you this exhibition match up.
Penny Barber is paired up with new cummer, Vivi Marie. They take on season 11 seasoned vets, Yasmine Loven and Lea Lexis. Penny Barber single handily carries this match but is it enough to get the win?
title: Pre-Season Tag Match up with all our Brats
